data.description:
Welcome to this super cute 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom gem that's sure to steal your heart! From the moment you step inside, you'll be greeted by the elegance of this thoughtfully designed residence. This home boasts a host of impressive features that make it the perfect place to call home.
The heart of the house, the open kitchen, is a chef's dream. It showcases granite counters, stainless steel appliances, and darker cabinets that elevate the cooking experience. Enjoy your meals at the breakfast bar. The kitchen seamlessly flows into the family room and dining area, creating a welcoming and harmonious living space. Don't miss this one.
